        </a>
        <a href="/reading-time-calculator" class="p-4 bg-surface rounded-lg border border-gray-100 hover:border-brand-pink hover:shadow-md transition-all">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-brand-orange">Reading Time Calculator</h3>
